data.description: Historic Capital Heights bringing to you a SOLID BUILT - 3 Bedroom 1 Bathroom - Brick home with all the new bells and whistles just in time for the Holiday Season. The Holidays will be brighter and family fun will be easier in this home that offers EVERYTHING ONE COULD DESIRE!!!! New Architectural Roof, New Lifeproof LVP flooring, New Countertops in the Kitchen, New Bathroom Vanity, New Window Blinds along with new plumbing and electrical fixtures too! This home will also have a new refrigerator, new stove, and a new HVAC system installed prior to closing. Dining, entertaining, relaxing, hosting, and enjoying everyday life will be a breeze in this WELL RENOVATED HOME! Do not miss out on this oppotunity!!!
